<div class="documentation_section_title">
  <%= tr("Branding Guidelines") %>
</div>

<div class="documentation_section">
  <p>
  	
  </p>
  <h2><%=tr("Overview")%></h2>
  <p><%= tr("To avoid confusion between Geni and your own site, service, product, or application, please follow these guidelines:") %></p>
  <ul class="standard_list">
    <li><%= tr("You may not use the word [bold: Geni] in the name of your product.") %></li>
    <li><%= tr("Please include a disclaimer that indicates that you are a separate entity from Geni. E.g., This application uses the Geni API but is not endorsed, operated, or sponsored by Geni, Inc.") %></li>
    <li><%= tr("Your own product's logo should be sufficiently different from Geni's logo as to avoid confusion.") %></li>
  </ul>

<h2><%= tr("Logos and Branding") %></h2>

<h3 class="mtl"><%= tr("When to include a Geni logo") %></h3>
<ul class="standard_list">
  <li>
    <%= tr("When displaying Geni content, display a Geni logo as the source of the content.") %>
    <%= tr("Where possible, link back to the content on [link: geni.com]", nil, :link => ["http://geni.com"]) %>.
    <%= tr("A Geni logo is [bold: not] required when displaying private user content to authenticated Geni users.") %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <%= tr("When requiring users to authenticate with Geni, include a Geni logo on the login screen, adjacent to the login form.") %>
    <%= tr("The submit button should read either [bold: Log in with Geni] or [bold: Connect with Geni].") %>
  </li>
  <li><%= tr("Optionally, you may also include a Geni logo on the start screen or home page of your product.") %></li>
</ul>

<h3 class="mtl"><%= tr("How to use the Geni logo") %></h3>
<ul class="standard_list">
  <li><%= tr("The logo should be an active link to [link: geni.com].", nil, :link => ["http://geni.com"]) %></li>
  <li><%= tr("The Geni logo should be less prominent than the logo of your own product.") %></li>
  <li><%= tr("You may not modify the provided logos other than to adjust their size. Do not edit, alter, truncate, filter, obstruct, distort or add content to the logo.") %></li>
  <li><%= tr("The logo should be displayed at a minimum size of 100 pixels wide and 40 pixels tall.") %></li>
  <li>
    <%= tr("The logo should be surrounded by sufficient whitespace to distinguish it from surrounding content.") %>
    <%= tr("The width of this whitespace should be at a minimum equal to the size of the dot on the letter i in the Geni name.") %>
    <div class="mtm mll"><%=image_tag("/platform/images/whitespace.png")%></div>
  </li>
</ul>

